<h2>Ice Activities in Lapland</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13068461/finland_levi_snowshoeing.jpg" alt="snowshoehero" data-udi="umb://media/3ddb8ffa2bfa4a8580cca14020f48e18" /></p>
<p>There are so many fun things to do whilst on holiday in Lapland, whether you are staying as a group of friends or as a family with children of all ages. From giving show-shoeing a try so you can view the wilderness around you or perhaps a race around the course in an ice-karting competition. There is no doubt you will have a full and exhilarating week. </p>
